            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Hoc est <expan><abbr>palatiu</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> Minerv<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> <lb n="2"/>imperatoris <expan><abbr>civitati</abbr><ex cert="low">s</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>Menandre <lb n="4"/><abbr>C</abbr> <abbr>D</abbr> VII
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Material: Carrara-Marmor. Z. 4: statt C auch E oder O, statt D auch P möglich. (B): Sgubini Moretti: hec est palatium inerve / imperatoris civitati / Menandro / [3] P VII.</p>
            </div>
